headline: Will Court Nod for Select Edgio Asset Acquisition Boost AKAM Stock?
summary: The deal is likely to be accretive to AKAM, offering hundreds of new customers and potentially augmenting its revenue-generating capabilities.

headline: Invesco Convertible Securities Fund Q3 2024 Commentary
summary: Convertibles (as measured by the ICE BofA US Convertible Index) returned 5.28% for the third quarter, compared to the S&P 500 Index, which returned 5.89%.
